{"tid":311921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"500人送別「白板」九巴","createTime":"2017-07-07T04:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T07:36:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a87affdb5c45b024c1e34b5a806ca8eb4b2d2c","tid":311921,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170707/20081647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170707%2F20081647&d=1fbGqqnYAtLpJKAk2R%2BITcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=61548817\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170707%2F20081647&h=d2ea582e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170707/20081647</a><br />\n<br />\n500人送別「白板」九巴<br />\n<br />\n12,575<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n ■巴士迷昨擠滿尖沙嘴碼頭的行人路，圍着「白板車」拍照。王子俊攝<br />\n■巴士迷昨擠滿尖沙嘴碼頭的行人路，圍着「白板車」拍照。王子俊攝 <br />\n因白色外觀而被稱為「白板車」的丹尼士巨龍10米型號九巴昨日退役，九巴安排最後一架白板行走8號線，於晚上8時在尖沙嘴碼頭總站開出，大批巴士迷前來送別。<br />\n<br />\n巴士迷：陪伴成長<br />\n白板為第一代非低地台空調巴士，車身以白色為主，中間綴有紅色橫線。白板退役後，市民日後在馬路上只能看見金色和紅色的九巴。下午3時，已有近20名巴士迷在尖沙嘴總站排隊，他們鋪上報紙席地而坐，更預備飯盒和零食。<br />\n17歲學生梁先生稱他3時半已在霸位，專誠來到尖沙嘴總站送白板「最後一程」。他認為白板車速較新車慢，而且非低地台設計不便傷殘人士登車，難免需要被淘汰。22歲巴士迷謝先生特意從大圍到來乘搭白板車，他從1998年白板車出廠開始乘搭了接近20年，表示巴士陪伴他成長。他更攜帶了從拍賣區買下的8號巴士膠牌，在背後寫上「再見龍仔，白板車年代已完結」的字句。<br />\n至下午5時，人龍已超過200人，九巴派職員截龍。白板車於晚上8時到達尖沙嘴碼頭巴士總站，約500名巴士迷起哄歡呼，部份人跑出馬路圍住巴士拍照，場面驚險。<br />\n■記者鄭佩林  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n伊院兩癌病人體內遺留金屬通管絲<br />\n下一則<br />\n【2D睇】「紅燈籠」出沒注意！3架英倫風紅色九巴"},{"pid":"17724dcf7e9195f46a47028174c9aad04d851a0b","tid":311921,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0277da37bcc938b37538647c11242b47006d82d4","tid":311921,"uid":97863,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"其實鍾意一樣野冇問題的<br />\n如果冇影響到人的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我反而想知個車長會想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fe2bf3f8d0e8ede645cb8cc0e1223b9ad44368","tid":311921,"uid":90503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"走開 小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9538afb4aa75a92be7716c390c9cf751899c8393","tid":311921,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實鍾意一樣野冇問題的<br />\n如果冇影響到人的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我反而想知個車長會想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係條片最尾見到係街度D人同架車揮手拜拜,  我反而有 D 感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來年輕人係仲有感情既.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcbca0e7c8aa63e4143f20812ca96e3e4edb241","tid":311921,"uid":23832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:43:19.000Z","msg":"好撚多巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2455bc8fde418046eb61e8a3eb4e7f0b3e0638","tid":311921,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實鍾意一樣野冇問題的<br />\n如果冇影響到人的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我反而想知個車長會想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尋晚成班粗口橫飛又佔領馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1f4b2400e1f100966c9893b859f3916407992b","tid":311921,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"毒撚到呢"},{"pid":"db5af3d788d2b49e074b0e7c9abbe55e825c9291","tid":311921,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re